---
import Main from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Main
  title="About - Matthew Cali Web Developer"
  description="Learn about Matthew Cali, a skilled web developer specializing in Ruby on Rails, custom websites, and digital solutions that help businesses grow."
  keywords="about Matthew Cali, web developer, Ruby on Rails developer, custom websites, business solutions, web applications"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-purple text-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        About Matthew
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Passionate web developer helping businesses succeed through custom digital solutions
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main About Content -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gradient-purple rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-4xl">MC</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">
            Building Digital Solutions That Work
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            I'm a web developer with a passion for creating custom websites and applications that help businesses grow. With expertise in Ruby on Rails, modern JavaScript, and responsive design, I focus on building solutions that are both powerful and user-friendly.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Every project I take on is an opportunity to solve real business problems through clean, efficient code and thoughtful design. I believe in creating digital experiences that not only look great but deliver measurable results.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-purple-800 font-semibold">
              "I don't just build websites â€“ I create digital solutions that help businesses thrive online."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills & Expertise -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">
        Skills & Expertise
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">RR</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Ruby on Rails</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Expert in building scalable web applications with Ruby on Rails, including e-commerce platforms, content management systems, and custom business applications.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Ruby 3.3</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Rails 7</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">PostgreSQL</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">FE</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Frontend Development</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Creating responsive, interactive user interfaces using modern JavaScript, Stimulus, and CSS frameworks that provide excellent user experiences.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Stimulus</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Tailwind CSS</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Bootstrap</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">API</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">API Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Seamlessly integrating third-party services like payment processors, email systems, and business tools to create comprehensive solutions.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Stripe API</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">RESTful APIs</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Webhooks</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">DB</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Database Design</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Designing efficient database schemas and optimizing queries for performance, ensuring your application can scale as your business grows.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">ActiveRecord</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Redis</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">DV</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Deployment & DevOps</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Getting your application live and running smoothly with proper deployment strategies, monitoring, and maintenance procedures.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Heroku</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">AWS</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Git</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">UX</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">User Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Focusing on creating intuitive, accessible interfaces that make it easy for your customers to accomplish their goals on your website.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Responsive Design</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Accessibility</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">Performance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience & Background -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">
        Experience & Background
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">WD</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Web Development Professional</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                With years of experience in professional web development, I've worked on everything from small business websites to complex enterprise applications. My background includes building e-commerce platforms, content management systems, and custom business applications that serve thousands of users.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Enterprise Applications</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">E-commerce Platforms</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">API Development</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">PS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Problem Solver</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                I thrive on solving complex technical challenges and finding elegant solutions to business problems. Whether it's optimizing database performance, integrating third-party services, or creating intuitive user interfaces, I approach each challenge with curiosity and determination.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">System Integration</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Performance Optimization</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Technical Architecture</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">CL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">Client-Focused Approach</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                I believe the best technical solutions come from truly understanding your business needs. I take time to listen, ask the right questions, and ensure that every feature I build serves a real purpose for your business and your customers.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Business Analysis</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Requirements Gathering</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">User-Centered Design</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values & Approach -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">
        My Development Philosophy
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">Q</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Quality First</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            I write clean, maintainable code that stands the test of time. Every line is crafted with care, following best practices and industry standards to ensure your application is robust and scalable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">R</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Results-Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Every feature I build serves a purpose. I focus on creating solutions that drive real business value, whether that's increased sales, improved efficiency, or better customer experiences.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-purple rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">C</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Clear Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            I believe in keeping clients informed throughout the development process. Regular updates, clear explanations, and transparent timelines ensure we're always on the same page.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-purple text-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Let's Work Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Ready to bring your vision to life? I'd love to hear about your project and discuss how I can help your business succeed online.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "/contact"}
          class="btn-outline-white hover:bg-white hover:text-purple-600 text-lg px-8 py-4"
          >Get In Touch</a
        >
        <a
          href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "/portfolio"}
          class="btn-outline-white hover:bg-white hover:text-purple-600 text-lg px-8 py-4"
          >View My Work</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Main>